resources.string: Be Awesome! This Feb join the biggest happening in town

In order to celebrate the real glories of India, a Mega Youth Cultural Fest ‘La fête Gita’ is organized from 22nd-24th February 2019, in ISKCON Bangalore. Anyone aged between 18 & 30 from all corporate and educational institutions are invited to participate and cherish this grand event..
Hare Krishna Hare Krishna,Krishna Krishna Hare Hare!
